g.title: get_client_data
g.text: get the data from the user and generate the client side metadata for storing the information of each run.

g.title: acccess_static_server_files
g.text: the static files available and required for execution of PaleoCAR on the server.

g.title: extract_prism_data
g.text: get the prism data file on the server with precipitation values and extract the data for the input coordinates and save as a csv file.

g.title: exec_paleocar
g.text: execute paleocar for reconstruction of paleoclimate of the study region. Generate the timeseries graphs, and paleocar models of paleoclimatic reconstruction.
